{"tid":1451342,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[科學Be Water] H2O (水) 常壓下之密度變化","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:50:10.000Z","uid":45741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6a8c3727966c72b45120d06403951301ed84f58e","tid":1451342,"uid":45741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://oi66.tinypic.com/2w3dji8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Foi66.tinypic.com%2F2w3dji8.jpg&h=ed8795e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據維基百科 (維基=事實=真理=應該無可能錯=除非真係錯)<br />\n水份子最高密度係大約3.98度時出現 (常壓) 有讀過AL chemistry 應該都有學過 (唔肯定DSE)<br />\n<br />\n升溫又好,降溫又好, 都唔及3.98度時既密度高 (正常情況)<br />\n<br />\n以上泠知識<br />\n<br />\n大家可以考下身邊既朋友／家人／同事／街坊<br />\n<br />\n問下水（water/H2O) 係咩溫度密度最高？<br />\n常理答 = 零度以下 因為冰硬~<br />\n<br />\n點知原來 -10'C 同 20'C 既水密度係相近<br />\n所以話Be Water係一門學問，科學少少去睇，又係另一回事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}